uint8_t* pksav_gen2_misc_fields::p_rival_name

A pointer to the rival's name.

This value should be accessed with ::pksav_text_from_gen1 with a num_chars value of 7.

This value should be set with ::pksav_text_to_gen1 with a num_chars value of 7.
